    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrCamera_base.1.jpg\" width=\"1280\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231763/PxrCamera_base.1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330717929&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=720\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542231763/PxrCamera_base.1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330717929&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"720\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542231775\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrCamera_base.1.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542231763\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"f68e1592-760f-475d-a835-fd0a71ff2f3a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231763/PxrCamera_base.1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330717929&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=720 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231763/PxrCamera_base.1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330717929&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=720 1x\"></span><p /><p><strong>Natural</strong></p><p>Natural vignetting. When one, directions off of the primary camera axis will be darkened realistically. Wide-angle perspectives will show this effect more strongly. Setting to zero disables this and intermediate values will blend accordingly.</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrCamera_base.gif\" width=\"1280\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231763/PxrCamera_base.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330717929&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=720\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542231763/PxrCamera_base.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330717929&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"720\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542231778\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrCamera_base.gif\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/gif\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542231763\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"b33b911d-f60a-4ced-8941-312da772de8a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231763/PxrCamera_base.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330717929&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=720 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231763/PxrCamera_base.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330717929&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=720 1x\"></span><p /><p><strong>Optical</strong></p><p>Optical vignetting. Simulates light blockage due to a hood or other additional lens elements. With depth of field enabled, this creates cat's eye bokeh. However, it also increases image noise.</p><p><br/></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"OpticalVignetter.gif\" width=\"1280\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231763/OpticalVignetter.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330717929&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=720\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542231763/OpticalVignetter.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330717929&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"720\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542231781\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"OpticalVignetter.gif\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/gif\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542231763\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"6e96a182-fc38-4d34-adae-50913bf8187f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231763/OpticalVignetter.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330717929&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=720 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542231763/OpticalVignetter.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330717929&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=720 1x\"></span><p />"
    }
